trans-unit.source: Provides data for <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoving"></xref> and the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoved"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoving"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoved"> </xref> hendelser.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoving> event occurs when the user is moving the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoving>hendelsen oppstår når brukeren glidende den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoving>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoved> event occurs when the user finishes moving the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoved>inntreffer når brukeren er ferdig med å flytte den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter.SplitterMoved>

trans-unit.source: The SplitterEventArgs class specifies the position of the mouse pointer and the position of the upper-left corner of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SplitterEventArgs angir plasseringen av musepekeren og plasseringen av øverste venstre hjørne av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SplitterEventArgs"></xref> class with the specified coordinates of the mouse pointer and the coordinates of the upper-left corner of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Splitter"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SplitterEventArgs"> </xref> klassen med de angitte koordinatene til musepekeren og koordinatene for øvre venstre hjørne av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Splitter"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The x-coordinate of the mouse pointer (in client coordinates).
trans-unit.target: X-koordinaten for musepekeren (i klienten koordinater).

trans-unit.source: The y-coordinate of the mouse pointer (in client coordinates).
trans-unit.target: Y-koordinaten for musepekeren (i klienten koordinater).
